Usage: write_extraction_spec [-help] [-no_design_data] [-out_dir {dir_name}]
                             [-rc_corners {rc_corner}]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-no_design_data         # Specifies whether design data to be saved or not (by
                        # default data will be saved.) (bool, optional)
-out_dir {dir_name}     # Specifies the location of output directory (by
                        # default go to a directory name starting with
                        # tmp_qrc_.) (string, optional)
-rc_corners {rc_corner} # Specifies the rc_corners to include in the extraction
                        # spec ((rc_corner)+, optional)